
<h1 class="govuk-heading-l datagovuk-heading-l">State-funded schools inspections and outcomes</h1>

<section class="govuk-section datagovuk-section">
  <p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">Get Ofsted’s official statistics on the inspections and outcomes of state-funded schools and academies in England since 2019. The statistics are published twice a year and include:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet datagovuk-list datagovuk-body">
  <li>the main findings</li>
<li>tables, charts and individual school-level data</li>
<li>a quality and methodology report</li>

</ul>
<p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">There are also datasets for inspections and outcomes management information, Parent View data, transparency data, FOI requests, Five-Year Ofsted Inspection Data, and data before September 2019.</p>
</section>


<div class="govuk-inset-text datagovuk-feedback-inset-text">
